trans-unit.source: Each <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflict" /> represents a conflict between items being deployed by a SharePoint project item and items on the SharePoint site.
trans-unit.target: 每个 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflict" /> 表示 SharePoint 项目项所部署的项与 SharePoint 站点上的项之间的冲突。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflictCollection> object is returned by the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.DeploymentStepStartedEventArgs.Conflicts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.

If you determine that a deployment conflict exists when a SharePoint project item is being deployed, use the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflictCollection.Add%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to notify Visual Studio of the conflict and to specify the method that Visual Studio will call to resolve the conflict.
trans-unit.target: 如果你确定部署冲突存在 SharePoint 项目项部署时，使用<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflictCollection.Add%2A?displayProperty=fullName>方法来通知 Visual Studio 的冲突和指定 Visual Studio 将调用来解决冲突的方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflictCollection.Add%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method returns an <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflict> object that represents the new deployment conflict.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflictCollection.Add%2A?displayProperty=fullName>方法返回<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflict>表示新的部署冲突的对象。

trans-unit.source: For an example, see [How to: Handle Deployment Conflicts](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-handle-deployment-conflicts.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关示例，请参阅[如何： 处理部署冲突](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-handle-deployment-conflicts.md)。

trans-unit.source: The description of the deployment conflict.
A delegate that can resolve the conflict.
The delegate must have a Boolean return value and a single parameter of type <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" />.
trans-unit.target: 代理必须有一个布尔返回值和一个 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 类型的单个参数。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the user should be prompted before the <c>resolve</c> delegate is executed; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果在执行 <c>resolve</c> 委托之前应提示用户，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Adds a new <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflict" /> object to this collection.
trans-unit.target: 将新的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflict" /> 对象添加到此集合中。

trans-unit.source: A new object that represents the deployment conflict.
trans-unit.target: 表示部署冲突的新对象。

trans-unit.source: For an example that demonstrates how to create an <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflict> object to handle a deployment conflict, see [How to: Handle Deployment Conflicts](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-handle-deployment-conflicts.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关示例，演示如何创建<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Deployment.IDeploymentConflict>对象处理部署冲突，请参阅[如何： 处理部署冲突](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-handle-deployment-conflicts.md)。
